title: Turbo.Fiesta.v1.0
description:
###################################################

Turbo Fiesta v1.0 *Precracked*

###################################################

DEVELOPER: Aliasworlds Entertainment
PUBLISHER: I-play
DATE: 11/09/08

Selling burritos and nachos to space tourists? It's just crazy
enough to work! Rebecca and Robert are taking their fast food
empire to totally new heights! Turbo Fiesta proves that there's
no place these two can't go to serve up a tasty treat! Third in
the hugely popular Turbo series, Turbo Fiesta is what happens
when south of the border cuisine rockets into orbit! Upgrade
your restaurant and chain together multiple actions to activate
the all-new fiesta mode!

The full version of Turbo Fiesta features:

* 60 fast-moving, fast-food levels
* 6 puzzling "pipeworks" mini-games
* Lots of upgrades and power-ups


Minimum Requirements

Windows XP/Vista
800 GHz processor
512 MB RAM
DirectX 8
32 MB video RAM
295 MB free disc space
